{"tid":966260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[習博士] 歷任中國國家主席學歷大比較，習近平是學歷最高的國家領導人","createTime":"2019-01-02T16:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T16:12:23.000Z","uid":155095,"like":194,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"2a7fffe08aed7e3212f23299d9b05e3d29da1649","tid":966260,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"毛澤東：湖南省立第一師範學校畢業<br />\n<br />\n劉少奇：蘇聯東方勞動者共產主義大學畢業<br />\n<br />\n董必武：東京私立日本大學法律系畢業<br />\n<br />\n李先念：湖北黃安2年私塾畢業<br />\n<br />\n楊尚昆：蘇聯莫斯科中山大學畢業<br />\n<br />\n江澤民：國立中央大學、交通大學畢業<br />\n<br />\n胡錦濤：清華大學水利系畢業<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">習近平</span></span>：清華大學馬克思主義<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">法學博士</span></span>畢業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wC1BF5dmAMA/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FwC1BF5dmAMA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=20b0de01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05f96c702ce289bdd9f70c12d4955cb5d5d62bd8","tid":966260,"uid":155095,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:00:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>畢業論文</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/dynimagecache/0/91/405/229/1024/578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/20130104075546938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fdynimagecache%2F0%2F91%2F405%2F229%2F1024%2F578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2F20130104075546938.jpg&h=11ba5625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>論文導師</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20171105/e58ea8f1e241446b88226d62a30c9ae6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20171105%2Fe58ea8f1e241446b88226d62a30c9ae6.jpeg&h=99f382d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c093d8123d714ea8a1b048bb92a2835c2ee4fec8","tid